0228637-e-35-div2-15">Why Vote in Authoritarian Elections? When Do Post-Electoral Protests Evolve into Nonviolent Revolution?</a></li><li class="div2"><a href="#acrefore-9780190228637-e-35-div2-16">Public Opinion and Protest in the Internet Age</a></li></ul></li><li class="sections"><a href="#acrefore-9780190228637-e-35-div1-5">Conclusion</a></li><li class="bibliography "><a href="#acrefore-9780190228637-e-35-bibliography-0001">References</a></li><li class="notes"><a href="#notes">Notes</a></li></ul><ul class="non-toc"><li class="related-link"><a href="#RelatedArticles">Related Articles</a></li></ul></nav>
		
